{"tid":299674,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有沒人覺得同人展開一段新關係好辛苦","createTime":"2017-06-27T09:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T14:37:17.000Z","uid":120095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63fb789fe964343810305166b6c20aefde35c6dc","tid":299674,"uid":120095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"分手半年，曾經迫自己試下同其他女仔發展，結果只係感覺到自己好攰唔想同人有更深入發展。<br />\n<br />\n當見到身邊個個男仔朋友好響住同積極追女仔既時候，我只係感覺到展開關係係一件辛苦事情。<br />\n<br />\n究竟有沒巴絲同我有相同感覺?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fd0c5a528519781057971bedb69a5f896de45c","tid":299674,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7672f3f9651404e0b6ac945b3262da9c0a5d76c8","tid":299674,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"係好撚攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610236788388b49c2e9c8b1a2fa79510313a4721","tid":299674,"uid":120095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>孤獨一生囉咁</blockquote><br />\n有覺悟"},{"pid":"6cd59202e101e70e945d1e3199746edc61af87b4","tid":299674,"uid":120095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係好撚攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a33f644fe678ab0e8beb62b020ba76ca7fc0489","tid":299674,"uid":62373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"真的提唔起勁"},{"pid":"e33557d2704fabd5864769dfbeebd13bfb594a3f","tid":299674,"uid":120095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真的提唔起勁</blockquote><br />\n建立一段關係，不論係朋友定男女朋友，都意昧住有多小維繫關係既責任，而我就係好怕呢種責任"},{"pid":"fa1e3cf8f9634ab88f6e6d54bdfbffb8d22e2229","tid":299674,"uid":312